title: to play dubstep live
pid: ac286e46-99bd-4f31-9fb8-66abde6b1911
body: |2-
  The wub voice has a pitch and a wub frequency.
  To control its pitch, use an ordinary pitch grid,
  plus a control of how long the slides take,
  which is anchored to time between two
  (historical, can be not most recent) pitch presses.

  The wub freq is anchored to the click, and uses a fraction input.
